# Keeps the data-lake root tracked while the bulk of /data is gitignored.
#
# This is the local mount for VQ__DATA__LAKE_ROOT (default `/data`). The HistoryReader serves
# backtest feeds AND live warm-up from here — identical in both, so indicators warm up the same way
# (docs/ARCHITECTURE.md §7, §10). Bulk Parquet partitions are ignored by .gitignore; only this
# placeholder and data/sample/ are committed.
